my usual routine,</b>

231
00:20:04,370 --> 00:20:07,707
<b>so I just sat there.</b>

232
00:20:09,042 --> 00:20:13,087
<b>I thought to myself,
now that I've taken on</b>

233
00:20:13,129 --> 00:20:16,966
<b>my mentor's goal,
what do I have</b>

234
00:20:17,008 --> 00:20:20,761
<b>to do to survive 99 games?</b>

235
00:20:23,890 --> 00:20:26,350
<b>One step at a time.</b>

236
00:20:27,393 --> 00:20:30,646
<b>One step at a time.</b>

237
00:20:30,688 --> 00:20:33,941
<b>I started small
and cleaned my place.</b>

238
00:20:33,983 --> 00:20:37,737
<b>When I was done,
there was one last step.</b>

239
00:20:39,906 --> 00:20:45,078
<b>As far as age goes, I can still
pass as a high school student.</b>

240
00:20:45,119 --> 00:20:49,289
<b>But for some reason,
I still felt weird.</b>

241
00:20:50,332 --> 00:20:52,334
<b>Since graduating
middle school,</b>

242
00:20:52,376 --> 00:20:54,670
<b>I've been floating
through life.</b>

243
00:20:54,712 --> 00:20:56,964
<b>I was ashamed
of being seen outside,</b>

244
00:20:57,006 --> 00:21:00,134
<b>so I stopped going
out in the daytime.</b>

245
00:21:00,176 --> 00:21:03,303
<b>[children laughing in distance]</b>

246
00:21:13,814 --> 00:21:17,068
<b>I smelled
the osmanthus blooming.</b>

247
00:21:21,739 --> 00:21:27,620
<b>The sun was setting, and I felt
its fading warmth on my back.</b>

248
00:21:29,247 --> 00:21:33,876
<b>I walked and kept walking.</b>

249
00:21:39,465 --> 00:21:43,177
<b>From now on, I'm going to live
in this world as a player</b>

250
00:21:43,219 --> 00:21:44,929
<b>full time.</b>

251
00:21:46,139 --> 00:21:49,100
<b>From now on,
my goal is to survive</b>

252
00:21:49,142 --> 00:21:51,811
<b>99 of these games.</b>

253
00:21:55,522 --> 00:22:02,863
<b>From now on, I play death
games to put food on the table.</b>

254
00:22:19,964 --> 00:22:22,925
<b>[gentle music, paper ruffling]</b>

255
00:23:26,446 --> 00:23:28,532
<b>[HAKUSHI'S AGENT]
I'm here to take you home.</b>

256
00:23:30,159 --> 00:23:31,244
<b>The game's over.</b>

257
00:23:31,285 --> 00:23:32,536
<b>Let's go.</b>

258
00:23:34,788 --> 00:23:37,124
<b>You can stop pretending
you're dead now.</b>

259
00:23:46,550 --> 00:23:49,011
<b>[HAKUSHI] Over already?</b>

